Do the weekly readings and come to lectures prepared, you'll be guaranteed to do well. The midterm was graded fairly and was based off everything covered in lectures and tutorials, no tricks. The final exam too covered everything that was discussed and done in tutorials, just a bit trickier than the midterm, but not difficult. Would take again.
